// SECRETS lets you create a list of hints to help you find the secrets 
// hidden in a level. This works with a special console command, 'secret', 
// which will print these hints in different colors depending on their status; 
// those that are found are in green, and the undiscovered ones in red.

// https://zdoom.org/w/index.php?title=SECRETS

// Each hint starts with '$'
// Followed by either an 's' for a sector or a 't' for a trigger
// At the end the sector number or TID, in this case 'sector 10' with ';'

[MAP01]
$s10; The secret lies behind the door. Use the red switch to open the door and grab some medals!

[MAP02]
$s0; No secrets here, but at least you know how to search for it.